  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nWhen you run tests with `truffle test --bail` the failed test that is bailed does not show information about emitted events during run of this test.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nRun `truffle test --bail` with test that fails and has emitted events in its run.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nDisplay the standard \"Events emitted during test:\" dialog\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nDirectly errors out without the information.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: macos\r\n* Ethereum client:\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.1.22\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v12.16.1\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.13.4\r\n",
